# Infinite Storyteller Project

## Overview
The Infinite Storyteller is an innovative writing project that combines elements of artificial intelligence, metaverse technology, and interactive storytelling. This document serves as a central reference point for the project's key concepts, characters, and world-building elements.

## Key Concepts
- Narrative AI: An advanced artificial intelligence system capable of generating and adapting stories in real-time.
- Metaverse: A fully immersive virtual reality environment where much of the story takes place.
- Cities of Light: Unique virtual locations within the metaverse, each with its own characteristics and challenges.

